# Enables verification of imports in Jest tests

## Usage

```JavaScript
// Jest config
{
  "moduleLoader": "jest-import-spy"
}
```

```TypeScript
import {collectImports} from 'jest-import-spy';

test('imports', () => {
  const imports = collectImports(() => {
    require('./sample');
  });
  expect(imports).toEqual(['lodash', './src/config']);
});
```
